item.title: About
item.description: I’m a software developer who seeks to help people. Pretty normal, isn’t it? Besides joining “late” to the party and for now (2017) with only two years of experience, I can already see what the future beholds and can’t wait to see what really comes next. I have a couple projects on the Play Store of my own, and another where I was paid to make which I’m not that proud of.
